Docs.returns:
true if the year, month, and day of the 
   exactly match the year, month, and day of ;
   otherwise, false.

true if the year, month, and day of the 
  is greater than the year, month, and day of ;
  otherwise, false.

true if the year, month, and day of the 
  is greater than or equal to  the year, month, and day of ;
  otherwise, false.

false if the year, month, and day of the 
   exactly match the year, month, and day of ;
   otherwise, true.

true if the year, month, and day of the 
  is less than the year, month, and day of ;
  otherwise, false.

true if the year, month, and day of the 
  is less than or equal to the year, month, and day of ;
  otherwise, false.
